description: This header file declares interfaces (functions) related to device telemetry data management, including getting and setting parameters by name and type, within a specific data model library.

methods.name: Telemetry_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for a device telemetry object based on parameter name.

methods.name: Telemetry_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for a device telemetry object based on parameter name.

methods.name: Telemetry_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for a device telemetry object based on parameter name.
